text: Rasmus Fyrpihl (born 12 April 1995) is a Swedish former professional ice hockey player. He played with hometown club Örebro HK in the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Fyrpihl made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Örebro HK during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish ice hockey left wingers Category:HC Vita Hästen players Category:Örebro HK players
